<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wèi wǒ yǔ wǒ fù jiā 迦南689</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wèi wǒ yǔ wǒ de fù jiā, xiàn shàng shú zuì jì. qí qiú shén shè miǎn kuān shù wǒ men de bù yì.
 chuán fú yīn gěi wǒ gǔ ròu zhī qīn. zhè gè shǐ mìng zuì jǐn jí, yě zuì jiān jù.
 yuǎn fāng de qīn rén a, wǒ men zhēn xiǎng niàn nǐ. shén de jiā xū yào nǐ, zhè gè shí dài gèng xū yào nǐ.
 wǒ men de guó tǔ lèi shuǐ wāng wāng. bèi qǐ shí jià tà tà shí shí bǎ zhǔ ài bō sā zài quán de.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>689</hymn_number>
</song>